OL,5, England is on course for the highest   
OL,6, number of school suspensions in a      
OL,7, single year, figures show.             
OL,9,FAccording to data from the Department  
OL,10,Ffor Education (DfE) there were almost  
OL,11,F264,000 suspensions in spring 2022/2023
OL,12,F- the largest number on record for one 
OL,13,Fterm.                                  
OL,15,FPersistent disruptive behaviour is the 
OL,16,Fmost common reason for children being  
OL,17,Fsuspended, or excluded, from school.   
OL,19,FTeaching unions say schools do not have
OL,20,Fenough resources to support pupils.    
